### John Henry Fashion - API Test File
### Sử dụng với VS Code REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)
### Cập nhật @baseUrl và @adminToken trước khi test

@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001
@adminToken = Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@userToken = Bearer YOUR_USER_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================================
### ADDRESS API - Không cần xác thực
### ============================================================

### Lấy danh sách tỉnh/thành phố
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/AddressApi/provinces
Accept: application/json

###

### Lấy danh sách quận/huyện theo tỉnh (id=1 = Hà Nội)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/AddressApi/districts/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Lấy danh sách phường/xã theo quận (id=1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/AddressApi/wards/1
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### VIETNAMESE ADDRESS API - Không cần xác thực (gọi external API)
### ============================================================

### Lấy danh sách 63 tỉnh/thành phố Việt Nam
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/VietnameseAddress/provinces
Accept: application/json

###

### Lấy quận/huyện của Hà Nội (code=01)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/VietnameseAddress/districts/01
Accept: application/json

###

### Lấy phường/xã của quận Ba Đình (code=001)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/VietnameseAddress/wards/001
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### ADMIN API - Yêu cầu Admin role
### ============================================================

### Dashboard Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard/stats
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Recent Orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard/recent-orders
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Recent Orders (limit 5)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard/recent-orders?limit=5
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Products List
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/products
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Products với phân trang
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/products?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Toggle Product Status
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE/toggle-status
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Orders List
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Orders với filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders?status=pending&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Update Order Status
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders/ORDER_ID_HERE/status
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Processing",
  "note": "Đang xử lý đơn hàng"
}

###

### Realtime Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/analytics/realtime
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Sales Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/analytics/sales
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Sales Analytics với date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/analytics/sales?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-12-31
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Users List
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Toggle User Status
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/USER_ID_HERE/toggle-status
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### System Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/system/health
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Banner by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/banners/BANNER_ID_HERE
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Banner
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/banners
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Title"

Banner Test
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="IsActive"

true
------FormBoundary--

###

### Update Banner
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/banners/BANNER_ID_HERE/update
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Title"

Updated Banner
------FormBoundary--

###

### Delete Banner
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/banners/BANNER_ID_HERE/delete
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

###

### Toggle Banner (enable/disable)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/banners/BANNER_ID_HERE/toggle
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

###

### Activate Banner
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/banners/BANNER_ID_HERE/activate
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

###

### Reorder Banners
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/banners/BANNER_ID_HERE/reorder
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newPosition": 1
}

### ============================================================
### LOGS API - Yêu cầu Admin role
### ============================================================

### Get Logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/logs
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Logs với filter level
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/logs?level=Error&page=1
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Logs với date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/logs?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-12-31
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Log by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/logs/LOG_ID_HERE
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### PERMISSIONS API - Yêu cầu Admin role
### ============================================================

### Get All Roles
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/permissions/roles
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Role Permissions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/permissions/roles/Admin
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Seller Role Permissions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/permissions/roles/Seller
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Search Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/permissions/users/search?q=john
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Assign Role to User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/permissions/users/USER_ID_HERE/roles
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roleName": "Seller"
}

### ============================================================
### NOTIFICATIONS API - Yêu cầu đăng nhập
### ============================================================

### Get Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Notifications
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Unread Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Notifications?unreadOnly=true
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Unread Count
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Notifications/unread-count
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Mark Notification as Read
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Notifications/NOTIFICATION_ID_HERE/mark-read
Authorization: {{userToken}}

###

### Mark All Notifications as Read
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Notifications/mark-all-read
Authorization: {{userToken}}

###

### Delete Notification
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Notifications/NOTIFICATION_ID_HERE
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### ============================================================
### SECURITY API - Yêu cầu đăng nhập
### ============================================================

### Security Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Security/check
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Security Logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Security/logs
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Change Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Security/change-password
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "OldPassword123!",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword456!",
  "confirmNewPassword": "NewPassword456!"
}

###

### Toggle Two-Factor Authentication
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Security/two-factor
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enable": true
}

###

### Send Two-Factor Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Security/send-2fa-token
Authorization: {{userToken}}

###

### Verify Two-Factor Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Security/verify-2fa-token
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "123456"
}

###

### Get Active Sessions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Security/active-sessions
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Delete Specific Session
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Security/sessions/SESSION_ID_HERE
Authorization: {{userToken}}

###

### Delete All Other Sessions (logout everywhere)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Security/sessions
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### ============================================================
### AUTHENTICATION (để lấy token cho các test trên)
### ============================================================

### Login (lấy session cookie)
POST {{baseUrl}}/Account/Login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@johnhenry.com",
  "password": "Admin@123!",
  "rememberMe": false
}

### ============================================================
### HEALTH CHECKS
### ============================================================

### Health Check tất cả
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Health Check chi tiết
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/detail
Accept: application/json
